#. List: 1
#. EDID: SFBGS047_co_Vehicle_MoonJumper
#. REC: COBJ:DESC
msgctxt "000001"
msgid "The Moon Jumper was developed by Stroud Eklund as an experimental long range expeditionary rover. Well armored, with a high capacity boost reserve for extended hovering capabilities."
msgstr ""

#. List: 1
#. EDID: SFBGS047_MoonJumper_Entered_MSG
#. REC: MESG:DESC
msgctxt "000003"
msgid "You have found the Moon Jumper! If you have already unlocked access to vehicles, it is now your active vehicle and is available for customization at any Ship Services Tech.\nTo unlock access to vehicles, visit a Ship Services Tech and ask to purchase a vehicle. This will give you access to the REV-8 and any other vehicles you may own."
msgstr ""

